I"Á<h2 id="learning-goals">Learning Goals</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Students understand the purpose of CI</li>
  <li>Students understand the mechanics of how CI works</li>
  <li>Students understand how CI factors into their workflow</li>
  <li>Students understand the purpose of CD</li>
  <li>Students are familiar with the idea of infrastructure management</li>
</ul>

